perfSONAR_PS::Services::LS README File
============================================

DESCRIPTION
-----------

The perfSONAR_PS::Services::LS module allows one to run a Lookup Service where
services can register the data they contain.

INSTALLATION
------------

 CPAN installation
 -----------------

    perl -MCPAN -e 'install perfSONAR_PS::Services::LS'

 Standard installation
 ---------------------

    Prerequisites:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

